  "instructions": [
    "Season the beef steak with salt, pepper, and black pepper.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a grill pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Sear the beef steak for 3-4 minutes per side, or until it reaches your desired level of doneness.",
    "Transfer the beef steak to a plate and let it rest for 5 minutes before slicing it thinly.",
    "Meanwhile, mix the pico de gallo sauce and chimichurri sauce in a bowl.",
    "Add the sliced beef steak to the bowl and toss it with the sauce until it's well coated.",
    "Serve the beef steak hot, garnished with fresh parsley and a sprinkle of chili powder.",
    "If using candy, sprinkle it on top of the beef steak before serving."
